  "text": "A 2.5 kb human fetal brain Fe65 cDNA clone, clone HB6, was labeled with biotin-11-dATP and hybridized to metaphase chromosomes derived from a normal male individual using the method of Edelhoff et al. [CITATION_1] . Hybridized chromosome spreads were processed for immunofluorescence, visualized and photographed using fluorescence photomicroscopy.",
